{"tid":1323614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］民陣稱警方提議將721大遊行改到8月舉行","createTime":"2019-07-16T09:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T13:20:09.000Z","uid":22556,"like":6,"dislike":155,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee01405251e5ac2f67f1f145d83f96620396460","tid":1323614,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"民陣申請在星期日晚上在金鐘政府總部外集會，要求政府成立獨立調查委員會。民陣下午和警察開會，警方稱基於公共安全考慮，建議將集會改期至8月。民陣表明拒絕，提出反建議在20或21日改為由銅鑼灣遊行到金鐘或中環。召集人岑子杰見記者強調，將集會改為遊行，已是提供彈性予警方考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065728&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=d5778a32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065728&h=d2f04d29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065728</a>"},{"pid":"5acfe6327f846cb5f674b60673ac280891d44b40","tid":1323614,"uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"民陣遊行可以繼續由銅鑼灣行去金鐘, 不阻礙自由活動<br />\n<br />\n和理非遊行好講象徵意義.  <br />\n遊行大部份人都唔係常客, 點同佢地解釋點解要由金鐘行去銅鑼灣?<br />\n<br />\n而且, 銅鑼灣行去金鐘, 都不會阻礙自由活動. 我諗71果時, 唔少運登仔都無跟遊行隊, 自由活動, 都無咩大問題.<br />\n<br />\n和理非同自由行繼續發揮民間智慧, 相信唔會出問題.  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JqmOToN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqmOToN.jpg&h=5d2d04e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6737586452254dfe2e98c95185b0fdb28db6b5ae","tid":1323614,"uid":37869,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"你咪唔好出不反對通知書囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f32907713f58d302f3aeb2ee6594bc2146233d","tid":1323614,"uid":247892,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:58:22.000Z","msg":"幾時輪到你話事<br />\n好fd呀家陣?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbea16e5a3df125665e4a